The paper focuses on image classification using deep learning approaches, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses distributed computing and scalability, which suggests that it may also belong to the distributed computing (cs.DC) and data structures (cs.DS) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions feature extraction and selection, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
